    <div class="card border-info mb-3">
        <h2>Fine Wines - Group Project</h2>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">
                Timothy Fine has taken over the running of his family’s vineyard in 2013. Mr. Fine decided to register the vineyard
                under the trading name Fine Wine Distributors (Pty Ltd.) Fine Wines vineyard is an expanding farm that grows both white and red grapes.
                Once harvested, these grapes are used to produce increasingly popular wines. Fine Wines has started to export a limited number of wines 
                to Europe and Asia in 2017. With the wine’s growing brand and popularity, the company requires a system that can aid the company’s 
                growing progress.  <br />
                To accommodate the company''s growth our development group was contacted to create a custom information system that is web based
                for internal and external requirements.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-2">
